      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS to deliver a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. This example has been fastidiously maintained with preventative rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement already addressed. The suspension geometry is dialed in with Bilstein dampers, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. The aesthetic condition is flawless, with original paint depth and an interior free of typical wear. A mechanically sound, concours-ready specimen for the purist.",
